    "The dependent variable (y) represents commercial potential, classified to 10.5%.",
    "It is important to recall that our measure is based solely on the text of the abstracts.",
    "This means that only words can explain the commercial potential in our model, leaving 90% to 95%",
    "of the variation in commercial potential scores explained by the remaining words in the abstracts and their interactions.",
    "To address this issue, we devised a novel experimental method, presented in the next section."
